- Nice to meet you.

164
00:12:12.524 --> 00:12:13.901
- …enjoy your flights.
- Bye. all.

165
00:12:13.984 --> 00:12:15.861
- Get home safe. Have a safe flight.
- Bye!

166
00:12:15.944 --> 00:12:16.945
Bye-bye.

167
