00:16:19.354 --> 00:16:20.480
Yeah. that was close.

214
00:17:26.797 --> 00:17:28.006
Good evening. Mr. Sugar.

215
00:17:28.507 --> 00:17:29.508
Good evening. Elinor.

216
00:17:30.092 --> 00:17:31.343
