00:19:25.749 --> 00:19:30.045
No. I called Jonathan to catch up.
and he gave me your new number.

233
00:19:30.629 --> 00:19:32.840
No. no. no. I… I didn't go.

234
00:19:34.091 --> 00:19:35.092
