253
00:21:19.404 --> 00:21:20.656
All right.

254
00:21:21.406 --> 00:21:24.535
Yeah. the hospital should've released.
Chuy's belongings to his grandmother.

255
00:21:25.202 --> 00:21:26.828
so ask her if you can check his phone.

